  "description": "<p style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">\n\t<img src=\"http://n1image.hjfile.cn/mh/2017/05/10/f0f42430887279bc3b88de3df1f0019d.jpg\" /></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">69. It&rsquo;s much easier to say &ldquo;Great idea!&rdquo;&nbsp;when a terrific solution has been put forward by someone on your team, than it is to take the time to explain why an employee&rsquo;s favorite brainchild isn&rsquo;t going anywhere except the circular file.</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">\n\t<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p1148857\" title=\"点击获得更好的阅读体验\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_video.gif\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">\n\t<strong>【结构分析】&nbsp;<br />\n\t</strong></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">\n\t&nbsp;<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">以逗号为切入点，得到一个比较结构 It&rsquo;s much easier to say &ldquo;Great idea!&rdquo;&hellip;than&hellip;。it 是形式主语，前半部分的真正主语由不定式结构 to say &ldquo;Great idea!&rdquo;&hellip; 充当，这里包含一个when引导的时间状语从句when a terrific solution has been put forward by someone on your team，使用了被动语态的现在完成时。后半部分真正主语为to take the time to explain&hellip;，explain后的宾语是why引导的宾语从句&nbsp;why an employee&rsquo;s favorite brainchild isn&rsquo;t going anywhere except the circular file。</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">\n\t<strong>【词汇】</strong></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">\n\t&nbsp;<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">terrific 极佳的，极好的----&gt;区分terrible 糟糕的</span></p>\n<p>\n\tput forward 提出</p>\n<p>\n\ttake time to do sth. 花时间做某事</p>\n<p>\n\tbrainchild 独创的观念；点子</p>\n<p>\n\tcircular file 比喻表达=waste basket 废纸篓</p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">\n\t<strong>【参考译文】&nbsp;</strong><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">当团队中的某个人提出了极好的解决方案时，说&ldquo;好主意&rdquo;要比花时间解释为什么一个职员最喜欢的想法最终被抛弃要容易得多。</span></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p1148857/#rela